{"tid":1956888,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台去年度收逾 1.2 萬宗投訴　兩主持因工作以外言行　暫停工作","createTime":"2020-04-03T13:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T13:52:07.000Z","uid":21141,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1da253eea01183d51dcbdd75049519d0495163a","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:25:52.000Z","msg":"反修例運動至今，香港電台屢被建制派及愛國人士批評，近日英文節目《The Pulse》更因訪問世衛官員，問及台灣世衛資格問題，被商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華批評，有違一個中國的原則及《香港電台約章》；多名立法會議員就《財政預算案》向商經局查詢，<span style=\"color: red;\">上個年度港台節目內容共接獲 12293 宗投訴，有兩名主持因工作時間以外的言行，接到投訴要暫停工作，其中一人因在個人社交平台，上載寫有被指為「散播仇恨或詛咒人家」字眼的揮春，而需停工。</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會最新文件顯示，過去 3 年，港台接獲合共 13205 宗投訴，其中去年度有 12293 宗涉及節目內容，另有 462 宗投訴行政事宜。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TiHCpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TiHCpa.png&h=13755bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，過去 3 年，港台接獲兩宗關於節目主持人於非節目時段的言論的投訴個案，均在反送中運動開始後出現。首宗個案在去年 7 月，投訴指一名電台及電視節目主持在一個非港台活動上，公開煽動他人犯罪，經雙方協商後該名主持暫停主持工作。<br />\n<br />\n另一宗個案在今年 1 月，投訴指一名電台節目主持在個人社交平台，上載寫有被指為「散播仇恨或詛咒人家」字眼的揮春，經雙方協商後該名主持暫停主持工作。<br />\n<br />\n12次因報道社會活動受傷<br />\n<br />\n在反修例運動中，<span style=\"color: red;\">港台職員去年有 12 次因報道香港社會活動而受傷，當中 6 次是被物件擊中受傷，例如 10 月 6 日被不明物件擊中導致左臉及左耳燒傷。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sJ0ZECA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsJ0ZECA.png&h=cd7c5f24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我繼續send email去睇同讚港台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nccu@rthk.hk"},{"pid":"d3fecac33e1265b4337facdeb94ca42ad8f351a4","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9bab055cd8fffac0f3ef7f9a3152d0193b4134","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafbd07a14e1cf9acc3a7b31dad119af59d78aec","tid":1956888,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d60614bcca1a1dcea60cb31bebbd5418dfdf63","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248d65b923f05eff2d8368b812dffd2275d3ca6b","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f994cb2169551b32c67c8e8072e4ca8370735f36","tid":1956888,"uid":21141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03fd987fca34146e05f21e76a9d95369df5f78c9","tid":1956888,"uid":19252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd79e40ac908772838f644bbae8263db3940ccb","tid":1956888,"uid":277640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T13:52:07.000Z","msg":"即刻做！"}]}